  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F/200°C).",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together pomegranate molasses, brown sugar, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the Portobello mushrooms with olive oil and season with the pomegranate mixture.",
    "Place the mushrooms on the grill and cook for 4-5 minutes per side, or until they are tender and caramelized.",
    "Transfer the mushrooms to a serving platter and drizzle with balsamic vinegar and olive oil.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve warm."
